            "title": "量化派暗盤大幅高開逾倍 股份明登場",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">羊小咩母公司量化派(02685)股份明天登場，今午暗盤高開逾倍，截至下午約4時40分，暗盤價約較招股範圍上限9.8元高約2倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"羊小咩官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/QG-M-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"羊小咩官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/QG-M-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">羊小咩官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">輝立交易平台顯示，量化派暗盤以25元開市，高招股價上限1.55倍；暫報28.5元，較招股價上限已高1.9倍。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">富途交易平台則顯示，量化派暗盤開報24.4元，現約報29.78元，較招股價上限高2.03倍。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15458133-%e9%87%8f%e5%8c%96%e6%b4%be%e6%9a%97%e7%9b%a4%e5%a4%a7%e5%b9%85%e9%ab%98%e9%96%8b%e9%80%be%e5%80%8d-%e8%82%a1%e4%bb%bd%e6%98%8e%e7%99%bb%e5%a0%b4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/02685.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-26 16:45:31",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "全日收市︱升幅收窄 恒指升33點報25928點 美團領跑 物流板塊受捧",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市午後升幅反覆收窄，未能企穩二萬六，重磅科股似有資金「換馬」，美團(03690)應聲彈升，另外物流板塊受捧，中集集團(02039)便A、H齊揚。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240826_FI_source-web_03690-GW-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240826_FI_source-web_03690-GW-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：美團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數今早甫開市即重越26000點，初段一度衝上26136點，將升幅擴大至241點後便乏力再上，早市中段更重新失守二萬六，其後開始在此關口爭持的局面，午後恒指再跌穿早市低位，尾市最低曾見25907點，升幅一度縮至僅12點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指最後收報25928點，升33點或0.13%。恒生科技指數升6點或0.11%，報5618點；國企指數升4點或0.04%，報9162點。主板成交降至2070.78億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15458044-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85%e6%94%b6%e7%aa%84-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8733%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125928%e9%bb%9e-%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%98%e9%a0%98%e8%b7%91-%e7%89%a9%e6%b5%81",
